{"tid":2022005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那核突style新景點「飛天之吻」…男女天仙升空做羞羞動作　網笑好刺激：口味超乎常人~","createTime":"2020-05-18T05:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T10:26:13.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f450490154782d9ef63143fe8e9cc18af7e26c48","tid":2022005,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/mnYE6j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FmnYE6j&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=4a3dc4f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/mnYE6j</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/5lRYk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F5lRYk7&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=9b27312c\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/5lRYk7</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=567982494122787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D567982494122787&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=cbdb2f8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=567982494122787</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSBwxxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSBwxxj.jpg&h=8f533bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在的旅遊景點究竟有多拼？ 近期，重慶市武隆區白馬山上的兩座人形雕像紅了。一男一女兩座色彩鮮豔的巨型雕塑，從地面旋轉上升到高空「接吻」，他們掌中托起的兩座飛行島上，讓島中遊客也在空中相遇。網友吐槽，「雕塑像巨人上菜」、「醜出天際」、「設計師口味超乎常人」。<br />\n <br />\n據《時代週報》報導，「飛天之吻」是計畫於今年6月正式開放，但在還未正式開放前，就已經在網路上紅了。這個項目屬於重慶市武隆區白馬山天尺情緣景區核心景點，高50多公尺，建立在1000多公尺高的懸崖上，是全球唯一的雙子互動式飛行島，遊客乘坐時可從空中俯瞰白馬山以及烏江景色。<br />\n <br />\n它的主體造型以武隆當地民間傳說-白馬仙子與茶仙女的愛情故事為原型，相傳兩人因愛觸怒王母，受貶化為白馬、仙女兩座仙山，隔烏江而望不得團圓。<br />\n <br />\n這個故事聽起來很淒美，可在最後呈現出的效果，非但沒有表現出神話傳說中的內涵，反而有些「煞風景」、「多少沾點土味」。<br />\n <br />\n曝光照片中，裸露上身的白馬仙子、生硬的動作造型和極為鮮豔的配色，有網友吐槽，「真是高大醜俗的人造景點，仙女和王子造型表情，」、「國內土味景點大軍再添一員」。但也有網友竟稱「竟然很想去體驗一下」，覺得「刺激過癮」，甚至「跪求」攻略。<br />\n <br />\n不過，更多的網友吐槽的是此設計「設計僵硬」，戲稱為「迷惑行為」，「本來產品體驗是可以的，千米懸崖，又是高空遊覽，但是這個外觀設計最後執行太弱了。」<br />\n <br />\n對於互聯網上的這些爭議，「飛天之吻」設計團隊負責人、北京綠維文旅綜合創意院楊凱院長表示，該項目落成的效果與原先的設計稿件並不一致，「在施工建設環節臨時出現的改動和調整，這也是我們沒有預見到的。」<br />\n <br />\n楊凱還提供了原設計稿，在原創設計稿中，能看出主要差距在於底座與服飾的呈現上，實地落實形象主要是實面彩塑外形，設計稿中則是漸變鏤空帶有裝飾性的的孔板處理，會相當降低大體量的視覺壓迫感。<br />\n <br />\n楊凱表示，「材質效果等跟原創設計差異很大，尤其是形式風格幾乎是對立性反差，目前的雕塑注重寫實，而設計中則更多是符合現代審美的半抽象式。」"},{"pid":"693b04dea732eb8884af5c637acdb513bffecaaa","tid":2022005,"uid":86819,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"D設計真係柒撚到無眼睇"},{"pid":"f744c3db7e6d1afad7611fe3e16ac8587df35555","tid":2022005,"uid":211947,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"係得支那人先整呢啲核突野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9e7712d00f7ef8b7be6cfde48599f8cbb25707","tid":2022005,"uid":198400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"Ultraman?"},{"pid":"940b897b5bbb99d1a45fe7774eb37b3145d5c2d9","tid":2022005,"uid":168400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a62da02aca1c491031ff1c1b958e5451af27586","tid":2022005,"uid":103405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒到唔敢睇"},{"pid":"1807ffbaf1e67eee0d844e0cd9fdc74646677573","tid":2022005,"uid":73569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左樣衰 仲要玩命"},{"pid":"e81c9b82dae2f9a43dfd5d58ce5950bf07616031","tid":2022005,"uid":6058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"條片上面個阿姐心諗：「快撚啲啦！好撚熱呀」"},{"pid":"edd3af71cf922f116406ec9b7ebdb00aa7c783af","tid":2022005,"uid":258770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"本來見到純白個concept art好似都ok 幾有藝術氣息<br />\n上左色變左紙紮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea68e8234580c851f0c4d02f47cd1fd51900d0fd","tid":2022005,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"以為虎豹別墅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e78880467f072bb18e833a655ca5896e285d2c","tid":2022005,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1807ffbaf1e67eee0d844e0cd9fdc74646677573","tid":2022005,"uid":73569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左樣衰 仲要玩命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"好全帶都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a198b7953208f457d5169a08d7359e5c2d1c195b","tid":2022005,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"點解啲配色可以咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dda39b54dec73e3e16d67b78b82a608add6143","tid":2022005,"uid":352066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f450490154782d9ef63143fe8e9cc18af7e26c48","tid":2022005,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/mnYE6j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FmnYE6j&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=4a3dc4f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/mnYE6j</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/5lRYk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F5lRYk7&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=9b27312c\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/5lRYk7</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=567982494122787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%